# Active Directory Penetration Testing Lab

## 📋 Project Overview

Complete Active Directory lab setup demonstrating three major Kerberos-based attacks:
- **LDAP Enumeration** - User and service account discovery
- **Kerberoasting** - Service account password cracking
- **ASREPRoasting** - Regular user password cracking

**Status:** ✅ All attacks successfully demonstrated

